Master items and Dimensions 7

Creating CategorySubCat dimensions

Click on Master item then click on Dimension and select Create new.

A dialog box will open. Select Drill-down for the dimension type and type Category under field.

Type Category under name then click to add it

Type Sub-Category and select it under field to add it to your drill-down

Add Product Name to the drill-down.

Lastly click on Create to create the drill-down dimension



Creating Map Hierarchy dimension

Click on Master item then click on Dimension and select Create new.

A dialog box will open. Select Drill-down for the dimension type and select Country under field.

Type and select State under field then click to add it

Type City and select it under field to add it to your drill-down

Next change the name to Map Hierarchy

Lastly click on Create to create the drill-down dimension

 


Creating Month dimension

Click on Master item then click on Dimension and select Create new.

A dialog box will open. Select Single for the dimension type.

Type and select Month (Order date) under field then click to add it

Click on create to create the dimension then click on close

 

 

Creating Year dimension

Click on Master item then click on Dimension and select Create new.

A dialog box will open. Select Single for the dimension type.

Type and select Year (Order date) under field then click to add it

Click on create to create the dimension then click on close

 

 

Creating Segment dimension

Click on Master item then click on Dimension and select Create new.

A dialog box will open. Select Single for the dimension type.

Type and select Segment under field then click to add it

Click on create to create the dimension then click on close
